+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CWyAHSvhowSePoEWzSswc2","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Here's the complete project structure analysis:\n\n## Project Structure Overview\n\nThis is a **Multi-tenant Analytics Dashboard API** project built with TypeScript and Express. The src/ directory is currently empty (only contains .gitkeep), ready for implementation.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Package.json - Dependencies and Scripts\n\n**File:** `/workspace/package.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"bench-analytics-dashboard\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"T8: Multi-tenant analytics dashboard benchmark\",\n  \"main\": \"dist/app.js\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint src/\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest run\"\n  },\n  \"keywords\": [],\n  \"author\": \"\",\n  \"license\": \"ISC\",\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.56.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.0\",\n    \"@vitest/coverage-v8\": \"^2.0.0\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^2.0.0\",\n    \"supertest\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"@types/express\": \"^4.17.21\",\n    \"@types/better-sqlite3\": \"^7.6.8\",\n    \"@types/jsonwebtoken\": \"^9.0.0\",\n    \"@types/supertest\": \"^6.0.0\",\n    \"@types/uuid\": \"^10.0.0\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"express\": \"^4.18.0\",\n    \"better-sqlite3\": \"^11.0.0\",\n    \"jsonwebtoken\": \"^9.0.0\",\n    \"uuid\": \"^10.0.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Build tool: TypeScript compiler (tsc)\n- Testing: Vitest with supertest for HTTP testing\n- Linting: ESLint with TypeScript support\n- Database: better-sqlite3 for SQLite persistence\n- Authentication: jsonwebtoken for JWT tokens\n- UUID generation for IDs\n\n---\n\n## 2. TypeScript Configuration\n\n**File:** `/workspace/tsconfig.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"target\": \"ES2022\",\n    \"module\": \"Node16\",\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"Node16\",\n    \"outDir\": \"./dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"./src\",\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"declaration\": true\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src/**/*\"],\n  \"exclude\": [\"node_modules\", \"dist\", \"tests\"]\n}\n```\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Strict mode enabled\n- Target: ES2022\n- Module system: Node16 (modern Node.js modules)\n- Output directory: dist/\n- Source directory: src/\n- Declaration files enabled (.d.ts)\n\n---\n\n## 3. Database Schema\n\n**File:** `/workspace/schema.sql`\n\n```sql\n-- Multi-tenant analytics dashboard schema\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS users (\n  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  email TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,\n  password_hash TEXT NOT NULL,\n  tenant_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  role TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'viewer' CHECK(role IN ('admin', 'viewer', 'editor')),\n  created_at TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT (datetime('now'))\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS events (\n  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  tenant_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  name TEXT NOT NULL,\n  properties TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n  timestamp TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT (datetime('now')),\n  user_id TEXT,\n  session_id TEXT\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS dashboards (\n  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  tenant_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  name TEXT NOT NULL,\n  owner_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  config TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n  created_at TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT (datetime('now')),\n  updated_at TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT (datetime('now')),\n  FOREIGN KEY (owner_id) REFERENCES users(id)\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS widgets (\n  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  dashboard_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  type TEXT NOT NULL CHECK(type IN ('counter', 'timeseries', 'breakdown', 'funnel')),\n  config TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n  position_x INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,\n  position_y INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,\n  width INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,\n  height INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,\n  FOREIGN KEY (dashboard_id) REFERENCES dashboards(id) ON DELETE CASCADE\n);\n\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_events_tenant ON events(tenant_id);\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_events_name ON events(name);\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_events_timestamp ON events(timestamp);\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_dashboards_tenant ON dashboards(tenant_id);\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_users_tenant ON users(tenant_id);\n```\n\n**Tables:**\n1. **users** - User accounts with roles (admin, viewer, editor), tenant isolation\n2. **events** - Analytics events with properties, timestamps, and user/session tracking\n3. **dashboards** - Named dashboards owned by users, tenant-scoped\n4. **widgets** - Dashboard widgets with types (counter, timeseries, breakdown, funnel), positioning\n\n**Indexes:** Optimized for tenant_id, event names, timestamps, and dashboard tenant queries\n\n---\n\n## 4. ESLint Configuration\n\n**File:** `/workspace/.eslintrc.cjs`\n\n```javascript\nmodule.exports = {\n  parser: '@typescript-eslint/parser',\n  plugins: ['@typescript-eslint'],\n  extends: ['plugin:@typescript-eslint/recommended'],\n  parserOptions: {\n    ecmaVersion: 2022,\n    sourceType: 'module',\n  },\n  rules: {\n    '@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars': [\n      'error',\n      { argsIgnorePattern: '^_', varsIgnorePattern: '^_' },\n    ],\n  },\n};\n```\n\n**Rules:**\n- TypeScript recommended rules enforced\n- Unused variables error (except those prefixed with _)\n- ECMAScript 2022 support\n\n---\n\n## 5. Vitest Configuration\n\n**File:** `/workspace/vitest.config.ts`\n\n```typescript\nimport { defineConfig } from 'vitest/config';\n\nexport default defineConfig({\n  test: {\n    globals: true,\n    testTimeout: 10000,\n  },\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. Project Requirements\n\n**File:** `/workspace/TASK.md`\n\nThe project requires building a multi-tenant analytics dashboard API with:\n\n1. **User Management** - Registration, login, JWT tokens, role-based access (admin/editor/viewer)\n2. **Data Ingestion** - Single and batch event collection with automatic tenant association\n3. **Query Engine** - Count, timeseries, and breakdown queries with tenant isolation\n4. **Dashboard Configuration** - CRUD operations for dashboards scoped to tenants\n5. **Data Export** - CSV and JSON export with tenant boundary enforcement\n\n**Technical Requirements:**\n- Express HTTP API\n- SQLite database (better-sqlite3)\n- JWT authentication\n- All protected routes must require authentication\n- Export `createApp` function from src/index.ts or src/app.ts\n- Strict TypeScript compilation (ES2022, Node16 modules)\n\n---\n\n## 7. Source Code Status\n\n**Directory:** `/workspace/src/`\n\nCurrently empty - contains only `.gitkeep`. Ready for implementation of:\n- Express app initialization\n- Authentication middleware and routes\n- User management endpoints\n- Event ingestion endpoints\n- Query engine implementation\n- Dashboard management endpoints\n- Export functionality\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\nThis is a **greenfield TypeScript project** with all configuration and database schema already in place. You need to implement the API from scratch in the `src/` directory. The project uses modern tooling (TypeScript 5.4, ES2022, Node16 modules) with strict type checking and ESLint enforcement."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ad6cc73 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 16863\ntool_uses: 14\nduration_ms: 20657</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"81d6606f-01b3-4de3-876b-c16d53bac7ec","uuid":"27426924-1247-4ce4-910b-59094518e81f","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the full project structure for this analytics dashboard API project. I need to understand:\n1. All files present (package.json, tsconfig.json, schema.sql, any existing src/ files)\n2. The database schema in schema.sql\n3. The package.json dependencies and scripts\n4. The tsconfig.json configuration\n5. Any eslint configuration\n6. Any existing source code in src/\n\nRead ALL 