+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01UWnG7rv7k79GDsFfeTyHAK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Non-interactive mode: using Autopilot. The design decisions are straightforward given the explicit requirements. Let me quickly work through the key decisions:\n\n**Design Decisions (Autopilot):**\n\n1. **Architecture**: Layered - routes → middleware → services → database. Standard Express pattern.\n2. **File structure**: Modular files by domain - `db.ts`, `auth.ts`, `routes/users.ts`, `routes/events.ts`, `routes/queries.ts`, `routes/dashboards.ts`, `routes/export.ts`, `app.ts`, `index.ts`.\n3. **Auth**: JWT with bcrypt-free approach (use crypto.createHash for simplicity since bcrypt isn't in deps). Actually, let me use crypto.pbkdf2Sync for password hashing since only native Node modules are available.\n4. **Tenant isolation**: Middleware extracts user from JWT, all queries filter by tenant_id from the authenticated user.\n5. **Database**: Initialize schema on app creation, pass db instance through app context.\n\nThese are all dictated by the constraints. Let me proceed directly to implementation via TDD."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":239,"cache_read_input_tokens":24006,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":239},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"81d6606f-01b3-4de3-876b-c16d53bac7ec","uuid":"f8dba0cc-6602-43c2-b968-04cc6c33e453"}
